"BRS Live Audio Archive 00-03 Vol.1 (SPAM-00002)

Burnt Ramen Studios is an underground venue and recording studio located in Richmond, CA. For over a decade there has been shows with various musical styles ranging from punk to metal to hip-hop to surf rock and many more. For more info on booking information, and history of this venue, please visit [www.burntramen.com] 

Product Info: These folders contain the years 2000-2003. This time frame is considered the prime time for punk and hardcore. Reviving these files took a year and half to put together, if you like this download and would like to help make volume 2 and 3 please donate (10$ recommended) via: 

Paypal @or Bitcoin 1BkszdFnxdyztAj7YiT1jhyVB5md6huZ1B"
